{"type": "article", "id": 15795, "title": "PERCY STOOLS 椅子", "description": "", "date": "2015-10-09T07:35:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 10, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000338vqQCwZz0oTXmhH1O.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这组糖果色的椅子来自墨尔本的年轻设计师 Ryan Pennings，完全采用 3D 打印技术。他运用了一种源于可再生资源的的生物塑料 PLA（聚乳酸）材料，让椅子的外形拥有流动感，紧凑密集。而椅子的内部则填充了一些松散的不规则的线条，相互对比，富有活力。由于固定的外形，这款椅子还能够并排起来组成颜色跳跃的方凳或长椅。<a href=\"http://ryanpennings.com/#/percy-stools/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261431393uklZNczeSF2OMHT.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"545\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261431402Fp8CgznrJTRcGex.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"545\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143141hDlVzBrS2LjJEFqs.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"515\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.62958435\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261431417vB9zjcquEMRoXb0.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"520\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.63569682\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}